snippet: With routine shows of emotion, the unbeaten Dominican Republic has led the World Baseball Classic in boisterous play, and had some American players grumbling.
abstract: Dominican Republic's dominant performance in the World Baseball Classic has been accompanied by boisterousness displays of emotion that are hallmark of sport in the country.
lead_paragraph: With routine shows of emotion, the unbeaten Dominican Republic has led the World Baseball Classic in boisterous play, and had some American players grumbling.
